if you want to control rolling startedgy and all 

    type: RollingUpdate
    rollingUpdate:
      maxUnavailable: 25%  --- one pod will be unavilable 
      maxSurge: 25%  ----- one pod will only create

[ec2-user@ip-172-31-31-136 ~]$ cat rolling.yaml 
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: myapp
  namespace: default
spec:
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
    rollingUpdate:
      maxUnavailable: 25%
      maxSurge: 25%
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: myapp
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: myapp
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: myapp
          image: nginx  
          ports:
            - name: http
              containerPort: 8181
          
